Nana Atiku, daughter of former Nigerian Vice President Atiku Abubakar, has gifted Nollywood actor, Zubby Michael, a plot of land as his birthday gift as he clocked 37 years. Taking to his Instagram page, Zubby shared a photo where he posed with Nana Atiku, revealing that he had been gifted a plot of land by her, a gift he tagged “best cake day gift ever.” The actor appreciated Nana, who is also a realtor, saying, “Best cake day gift ever. NANA ATIKU just gifted ME a plot of land in Abuja as a cake day gift @nanaatiku_kadi. I really appreciate this thanks and GOD bless.” Nana Atiku, under the comment of the post where she was tagged, wrote: “One love.” Nana also shared some photos with Zubby on her Instagram page as she celebrated him.She wrote: “Happy birthday to my favorite Actor. A Man with a heart of gold. May happiness never depart from you. May God keep opening your ways as you bless others. Am always proud of you. Happy birthday my brother. May Allah bless your new Age.” Rugged actor, Zubby Michael is currently a proud owner of a plot of land in the Federal Capital Territory, Abuja. A fan of the actor whom he identified as Nana Atiku gave him the plot of land to mark his birthday on Tuesday. Sharing the good news on his Instagram… In "News" Nollywood actor, Zubby Michael has surprised his personal assistant with a plot of land for his loyalty. The actor took to Instagram to share a photo of himself presenting documents of the land to his PA and then wrote: 'Just gave my P A a plot of land @syratouchmetu enjoy.'… In "News" Nollywood star, Uche Jombo, clocked 42 on Tuesday and her colleagues have taken to Instagram to wish the actress a happy birthday. Jombo had earlier taken to her page to announce her birthday as she shared snow-themed photos with the caption, “Happy birthday to me.” Taking to her Instagram story,… In "Entertainment"